2026-05-19T04:01:05.4274164Z 246            Harden Google Play Billing's proxy activities so the system
2026-05-19T04:01:05.4275007Z 247            cannot restore them from Recents or after process death with a
2026-05-19T04:01:05.4275824Z 248            stale Intent. The library's onCreate reads the PendingIntent
2026-05-19T04:01:05.4276630Z 249            extra without null-checking; if Android recreates the activity
2026-05-19T04:01:05.4277324Z 250            and the extra is missing, it NPEs on
2026-05-19T04:01:05.4278054Z 251            PendingIntent.getIntentSender(). noHistory + excludeFromRecents
2026-05-19T04:01:05.4278794Z 252            finishes the activity as soon as it leaves the foreground so it
2026-05-19T04:01:05.4279573Z 253            is never re-entered with a missing extra. Library 8.x adds its
2026-05-19T04:01:05.4280600Z 254            own configChanges absorber and a v2 proxy, both of which we
2026-05-19T04:01:05.4281254Z 255            preserve via tools:node="merge".
