2026-05-19T04:01:05.8063141Z 271            Harden Google Play Billing's proxy activities so the system
2026-05-19T04:01:05.8063483Z 272            cannot restore them from Recents or after process death with a
2026-05-19T04:01:05.8063794Z 273            stale Intent. The library's onCreate reads the PendingIntent
2026-05-19T04:01:05.8064124Z 274            extra without null-checking; if Android recreates the activity
2026-05-19T04:01:05.8064340Z 275            and the extra is missing, it NPEs on
2026-05-19T04:01:05.8064716Z 276            PendingIntent.getIntentSender(). noHistory + excludeFromRecents
2026-05-19T04:01:05.8065046Z 277            finishes the activity as soon as it leaves the foreground so it
2026-05-19T04:01:05.8065363Z 278            is never re-entered with a missing extra. Library 8.x adds its
2026-05-19T04:01:05.8065677Z 279            own configChanges absorber and a v2 proxy, both of which we
